    <abstract>
      <t>TRILL is a key technology for large-scale layer 2 networking within a data center, TRILL over WAN_(ToW) provides a scalable and simple solution that interconnect multiple TRILL networks to form a single TRILL domain using the currently deployed enterprise or service provider networks. This document provides an overview of this solution.</t>
